the database and API are two seperate things 

FastAPI app  ---- connects to ---->  PostgreSQL server



The PostgreAQL is running as a server on your computer 

FastAPI is another program 


Connection needs 5 pieces 


1. Host

2. port 

3. database 

4. user 

which postgresql user logs in 

5. password 

user password 

for example 

host: localhost
port: 5432
database: bar_ticket
user: postgres
password: your_password


the database URL looks liek this:

DATABASE_URL=postgresql+psycopg://postgres:your_password@localhost:5432/bar_ticket


what is postgresql+psycopg://

this is the driver 

psycopg driver 







- what the driver does?

your python code cannot magically speak to the driver itself ! 


so you need to install a driver 


pip install psycopg[binary] sqlalchemy python-dotenv



